Directed by Pandiraj.

Written by Pandiraj. Pandiraj. Pandiraj.

Cast Karthi(Gunasingam). Sathyaraj(Perunazhi Ranasingam). Sayyeshaa Saigal(Kannukuiniyal). Priya Bhavani Shankar(Poonkuzhali Chellamma). Arthana Binu(Aandal Priyadarshini). Bhanupriya(Panchamadevi). Soori(Sivagamiyin Selvan). Viji Chandrashekhar(Vanavan Madevi). Yuvarani(Samyuktha Rani). Mounica(Mangamma Rani). Deepa Shankar(Velunachiar Rani) .Chandru.Deepa.Dheeraj. Ilavarasu(Manikkam).Johnny.Fighter Karthi.Kennadiswami.Krishnamurthy.Jeevitha Krishnan.Manoj Kumar.Maaran.Mahendran. Indumathy Manikandan((as Indumathi Manigandan)).Manobala. G. Marimuthu((as Marimuthu)).Muthuraman.Panneer.Pandy Pasanga.Ponvannan.Muthu Ramalingam.Ranga.Eesakki Ravi.Rindhu Ravi.Saravanan.Selvam.Senthikumari.Shatru.Shiva. Soundararaja((as Soundara Raja)).Srimaan.Sriman. Suriya(Chief Guest).John Vijay.Yogi

Language Tamil.

Producer Suriya.

Production 2D Entertainment.
